<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Help</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon"
        href="https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/naruto/images/6/64/Favicon.ico/revision/latest?cb=20141014010210"
        type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="help.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/ae353bb49a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</head>

<body style="display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
        {{>header}}

        <div id="help">
            <div class="container">
                <header>
                    <h1>Naruto API v1 Documentation</h1>
                    <div class="twitter">
                        <i class="fa fa-github fa-2x"> </i>
                        <a class="search-queries-link" target="_blank"
                            href="https://www.github.com/sarveshtheabstractor">@sarveshtheabstractor</a>
                    </div>
                </header>


                <h4>Important details:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>No need to use CORS proxy or API key</li>
                    <li>Supports up to Unlimited Requests</li>
                    <li>Search terms are limited. Search for "naruto" or another character from this list ðŸ¡’ <a
                            href="/phrases" class="search-queries-link">search characters</a></li>
                    <li>Only GET requests allowed</li>
                </ul>
                </ul>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <h2>Search</h2>
                <p class="description">Returns a list of recipes for a specific query</p>
                <p>Path: <code>https://narutoforlifeapi.herokuapp.com/api/characters/</code></p>
                <h3>Parameters</h3>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Parameter</th>
                        <th>Required</th>
                        <th>Description</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>q</td>
                        <td>Yes</td>
                        <td>Query text. For example <span class="highlighted-text">q=naruto</span>. See the list of all
                            available characters ðŸ¡’ <a href="/phrases" class="search-queries-link">search
                                characters</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p>Example URL: <code>https://narutoforlifeapi.herokuapp.com/api/characters/q</code></p>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <h2>How to make request to this API</h2>
                <img src="./carbon2.png" style="max-width: 100%;" alt="request" srcset="">

                <h2>Response From the Server</h2>
                <img src="./carbon.png" style="max-width: 100%;" alt="response" srcset="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{>footer}}


</body>

</html>